  "title": "Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<p><strong>About the role</strong><br>\n<br>\nAre you a skilled Quantity Surveyor looking to join a dynamic construction company? Right Construction Pte Ltd, an established player in the construction industry, is seeking a Quantity Surveyor to join its team. This full-time position will see you playing a vital role in managing the financial aspects of construction projects, ensuring cost-effective and successful project delivery.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What you'll be doing</strong></p>\n<ol>\n  <li>Preparing detailed cost estimates and budgets for construction projects.</li>\n  <li>Monitoring and controlling project costs throughout the construction process.</li>\n  <li>Negotiating and finalising contract terms with suppliers and subcontractors.</li>\n  <li>Analysing and interpreting contract documents, drawings and specifications.</li>\n  <li>Preparing progress claims, variation orders and final accounts.</li>\n  <li>Providing commercial and contractual advice to project managers and site teams.</li>\n  <li>Identifying potential cost savings and value engineering opportunities.</li>\n  <li>Maintaining comprehensive project cost records and documentation.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What we're looking for</strong></p>\n<ol>\n  <li>Degree or equivalent qualification in Quantity Surveying or a related field.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years' experience as a Quantity Surveyor in the construction industry.</li>\n  <li>Strong understanding of construction contracts, cost management and project controls.</li>\n  <li>Proficient in using quantity surveying software and MS Office applications.</li>\n  <li>Excellent analytical and problem-solving skills.</li>\n  <li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills to liaise with stakeholders.</li>\n  <li>Attention to detail and ability to work to tight deadlines.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What we offer</strong><br>\n<br>\nAt Right Construction Pte Ltd, we are committed to providing our employees with a rewarding and fulfilling work experience. In addition to a competitive salary, we offer a range of benefits, including:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Opportunities for professional development and career advancement</li>\n  <li>Collaborative and supportive work environment</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>About us</strong><br>\n<br>\nRight Construction Pte Ltd is a leading construction company specialising in residential, commercial and industrial projects in the Singapore. Established in 1994, we have a strong track record of delivering high-quality, innovative construction solutions that exceed our clients' expectations. Our team of experienced professionals is committed to upholding the highest standards of safety, quality and sustainability in all our projects.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Apply now</strong><br>\n<br>\nIf you're ready to take the next step in your Quantity Surveying career, we'd love to hear from you. Click the \"Apply\" button below to submit your application.</p>",
